summary: Adds a full set of druid armor
descriptionHtml:
Perfect armor if you want to be a Neutral druid character. can be found in Whiterun near the Talos shrine.
ARMOR SET-
-Horker Skin Boots              -Evergreen Blade
-Spriggan Bark Shield           -Staff of the High Forest
-Predators Helm
-Amulet of Nature
-Neutral Druid Robes
-Mudcrab Shell Bracers
